OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FThis year's elections in the UK are
OL,7,Fmuch more important than you might
OL,8,Fthink - and the results could have a
OL,9,Fhuge impact in both the immediate
OL,10,Faftermath and in years to come.
OL,12,FOn May 7, millions of people in
OL,13,FEngland, Scotland, and Wales will
OL,14,Felect over 5,000 politicians in
OL,15,Felections that could produce a set of
OL,16,Fresults the UK has never seen before.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775743871
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FThe Welsh and Scottish national
OL,7,Felections could set a path for the
OL,8,Fbreakup of the UK, England's council
OL,9,Felections could decimate Labour and
OL,10,Fthe Conservatives, and the results
OL,11,Facross the board could be the end of
OL,12,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer.
OL,14,FWhat's happening where? And what's
OL,15,Fchanged?
OL,17,FIn England, elections are being held
OL,18,Ffor 4,851 council seats across 134 of
OL,19,FEngland's 317 council areas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775743871
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FThe areas include big cities like
OL,7,FLondon, Manchester, Birmingham and
OL,8,FNewcastle, as well as counties
OL,9,Fincluding Essex, Norfolk, and Suffolk.
OL,11,FFor the first time, people will be
OL,12,Fable to vote in person on the weekend
OL,13,Fbefore polling day, in trials that are
OL,14,Fbeing run in Cambridge, Tunbridge
OL,15,FWells and North Hertfordshire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775743871
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FAnother trial will allow people in
OL,7,FMilton Keynes to vote in a central hub
OL,8,F- a shopping centre - which will be
OL,9,Fopen to all residents, rather than
OL,10,Frestricting them to a single
OL,11,Fdesignated polling station.
OL,13,FThese trials will be the first time
OL,14,Fpolling booth voting has changed since
OL,15,F1872.
OL,17,FWhat is happening in Scotland and
OL,18,FWales?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775743871
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FIn Wales, the electoral system has
OL,7,Fchanged for the first time since its
OL,8,Ffirst devolved election in 1999.
OL,10,FThe number of Senedd seats up for
OL,11,Fgrabs is increasing from 60 to 96, but
OL,12,Fthe number of constituencies is
OL,13,Fdecreasing from 40 to 16, and each
OL,14,Fwill elect six politicians.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775743871
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FPeople in Wales will now only cast one
OL,7,Fvote, rather than the two in previous
OL,8,Felections - and ballot papers will
OL,9,Fonly display party names rather than
OL,10,Fcandidates. Previously, people were
OL,11,Fable to issue a vote for a candidate
OL,12,Fand another for a party.
OL,14,FIt's designed to create a fairer
OL,15,Fsystem where a party's number of seats
OL,16,Fmore closely aligns with their vote
OL,17,Fshare, but critics say it will benefit
OL,18,Fsmaller parties.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775743871
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FScotland, which is electing 129
OL,7,Fmembers to the Scottish parliament, is
OL,8,Fstill using the Additional Member
OL,9,FElectoral System, which Wales has
OL,10,Fscrapped, meaning Scots will cast two
OL,11,Fvotes - one for a candidate and
OL,12,Fanother for a party.
OL,14,FIn Scotland and Wales, 16-year-olds
OL,15,Fcan vote. The voting age in England
OL,16,Fwill still be 18 until the government
OL,17,Flowers it across the UK ahead of the
OL,18,Fnext general election.
OL,20,FDelayed elections
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775743871
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FSeveral elections are taking place in
OL,7,FEngland despite the government
OL,8,Fpreviously agreeing to postpone them
OL,9,Fdue to capacity issues.
OL,11,FHowever, a legal challenge by Reform
OL,12,FUK means they are still going ahead.
OL,14,FPoliticians elected in Wales and
OL,15,FScotland will make decisions that
OL,16,Faffect their whole country, while
OL,17,Fcouncillors in England only preside
OL,18,Fover their local areas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
