PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775743871
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FAll of these elections are critical
OL,7,Ffor the Labour Party and could be
OL,8,Ffatal for Starmer.
OL,10,FLabour at risk - the end of Starmer?
OL,12,FA poor performance in May really could
OL,13,Fbe the beginning of the end for the
OL,14,Fprime minister, who has insisted he
OL,15,Fwould never resign.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775743871
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FParties of government often perform
OL,7,Fbadly in mid-term elections - and
OL,8,Fthat's what Labour spinners will be
OL,9,Fsaying after the elections - but
OL,10,FLabour's dramatic fall from a
OL,11,Flandslide general election in 2024 is
OL,12,Fremarkable.
OL,14,FJust under two years ago, Labour
OL,15,Flooked set to dominate the UK. It was
OL,16,Fexpected to take Scotland back from
OL,17,Fthe SNP for the first time since 2007
OL,18,Fand was going to continue its winning
OL,19,Fstreak in Wales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775743871
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FBut Starmer's unpopularity means
OL,7,FLabour looks set to not win in Wales
OL,8,Ffor the first time, behind Plaid Cymru
OL,9,Fand Reform UK.
OL,11,FStarmer is so unpopular in Scotland
OL,12,Fthat in February, the leader of
OL,13,FScottish Labour, Anas Sarwar, held a
OL,14,Fpress conference demanding he quit as
OL,15,Fprime minister.
OL,17,FBut that did not shift the dial, and
OL,18,FLabour could end up with not only
OL,19,Ffewer seats than the Scottish National
OL,20,FParty, but Reform UK too.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775743871
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FIf Labour loses significant ground in
OL,7,FEngland, and fails in Wales and
OL,8,FScotland, it's likely his MPs will
OL,9,Fseek to replace him with either Angela
OL,10,FRayner, Wes Streeting, or someone else.
OL,12,FNationalist control - the breakup of
OL,13,Fthe UK?
OL,15,FStarmer's survival is not the only
OL,16,Fthing on the line here - results in
OL,17,FScotland and Wales could spark the
OL,18,Fbreakup of the United Kingdom.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775743871
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FIf Plaid Cymru and the SNP win their
OL,7,Felections, it would be the first time
OL,8,Fthat each devolved nation is run by
OL,9,Fnationalist parties that want to leave
OL,10,Fthe UK - along with Sinn Fein, which
OL,11,Fhas the most seats in Northern Ireland.
OL,13,FThe SNP says winning a majority in May
OL,14,Fwould be proof Scots want another
OL,15,Findependence referendum after they
OL,16,Fvoted to remain in 2014.
OL,26,@rD@[rr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775743871
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FPlaid wants independence for Wales as
OL,7,Fwell, but the nationalist party says
OL,8,Fit will not be calling for a
OL,9,Freferendum immediately if it wins in
OL,10,FMay.
OL,12,FLeader Run ap Iorworth says they need
OL,13,Fto prove themselves as a party that
OL,14,Fcan run Wales before campaigning for
OL,15,Findependence if it wins a second
OL,16,Fconsecutive election.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775743871
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FSinn Fein, which is in power in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland, also wants to leave
OL,8,Fthe UK however, that would be more
OL,9,Fcomplicated because of the Good Friday
OL,10,FAgreement.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FLabour, however, has already insisted
OL,18,Fthere will not be another referendum
OL,19,Fin Scotland and would be extremely
OL,20,Funlikely to allow one in Wales or
OL,21,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,26,@nD@Grr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775743871
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FHowever, if nationalist parties
OL,7,Fcontinue to win for years to come,
OL,8,Fcalls for independence will only grow
OL,9,Flouder.
OL,11,FReform and the Greens - the end of two-
OL,12,Fparty politics?
OL,14,FIt's been said since the general
OL,15,Felection in 2024 that the UK's two
OL,16,Fparty system could be coming to an end
OL,17,F- and these elections are a chance for
OL,18,FReform UK and the Greens to prove that.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30817
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775743871
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FReform UK's Nigel Farage has pledged
OL,7,Fto replace the Conservatives and Zack
OL,8,FPolanski says the Greens want to do
OL,9,Fthe same with Labour.
OL,11,FBoth parties are still considered
OL,12,Fsmall in the grand scheme of things;
OL,13,Fthey have very little representation
OL,14,Facross the UK - but by beating Labour
OL,15,Fand the Tories, they will show their
OL,16,Fsupporters an alternative could be
OL,17,Fpossible.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30818
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775743871
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FBut a lot is at stake for them too -
OL,7,Fif Reform UK fails to emulate its poll
OL,8,Frating in these upcoming elections,
OL,9,Fpeople might wonder whether their
OL,10,Fsupport has peaked and may start
OL,11,Fconsidering other parties.
OL,13,FIf the Greens perform poorly it could
OL,14,Fshow voters the environmentalists can
OL,15,Fonly win in pockets of the UK.
OL,17,FBoth parties are predicted to do well;
OL,18,FReform thinks it can win in Wales and
OL,19,FPolanski thinks he can turn London
OL,20,FGreen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30819
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775743871
OL,3,CLocal elections 2026 - What is at
OL,4,Cstake?
OL,6,FBut we can't forget the Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrats, traditionally the UK's
OL,8,Fthird party. They often perform well
OL,9,Foutside general elections when Labour
OL,10,For Conservative supporters want to try
OL,11,Fsomething else.
OL,13,FAside from the wider political
OL,14,Fimplications, the elections on May 7th
OL,15,Fare hugely important for choosing
OL,16,Fwho's in charge of things like
OL,17,Feducation and health in Scotland and
OL,18,FWales, and who will make local
OL,19,Fdecisions on things like road works
OL,20,Fand planning applications in England.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
